episodes.title: The Autobiography of a Yogi Under a Critical Microscope, EPISODE 2
episodes.description: After recounting his recovery from cholera and receiving a new spiritual vision of Iswara as Light while meditating, Yoganandadetails how concentrated speech can directly impact the human body.

episodes.title: The Autobiography of a Yogi Under a Critical Microscope, EPISODE 1
episodes.description:
In the very first chapter of his life story, Yogananda alleges that he was cured of Asiatic cholera at the age of eight years old becauseof a unique and blessed photograph of his parents’ guru, LahiriMahasaya.

This is episode 1 of 26. At end of each, we provide critical and skeptical analysis of the so-called miracle or paranormal event. Also forthcoming is a conclusion and an appendix.

episodes.title: The Autobiography of a Yogi Under a Critical Microscope, Introduction
episodes.description: This is the introduction to a book entitled The Skeptical Yogi: Yogananda's Autobiography under a Critical Microscope. Although I am a great fan of the book, since I first read it at the age of 11, over time it has become obvious to me that many of the so-called miracles in Yogananda's tale can be better explained more rationally and scientifically. This book is an attempt to do such.

episodes.title: Cult 101: John-Roger Hinkins, MSIA, and Getting Exposed
episodes.description: Gives a critical look at John-Roger Hinkins and MSIA. J.R. was formerly associated with Eckankar and later claimed he was in contact with Sawan Singh of Radhasoami Satsang Beas on the Inner Planes. Brief interview includes David C. Lane among others. Watch for Peter McWilliams, who later defected, blocking the camera.

episodes.title: Cult 101: J.R. being exposed on Geraldo's NOW IT CAN BE TOLD
episodes.description: Excerpts from the infamous television episode that exposed John-Roger Hinkins and MSIA. Includes Peter McWilliams BEFORE he defected and wrote LIFE 102 and a brief interview of David Lane

episodes.title: Arianna Huffington- Movement of Spiritual Inner Awareness
episodes.description: News excerpt from 1994, just after Peter McWilliams' book, LIFE 102: WHAT TO DO WHEN YOUR GURU SUES, came out and basically altered the governorship campaign of Michael Huffington. Basically shows Arianna Huffington fumbling when asked about her well documented association with John-Roger Hinkins.
